@startuml UC6: Reservation Change - Create Request Deadline Passed

!theme plain

autonumber

actor User
participant "System" as System
participant "Server" as Server

== Create Change Request ==

User -> System: Press "Order Change Request" Button
System -> Server: Request Create Change Request
Server -> Server: Check Order Ownership
Server -> Server: Check Change Deadline\n(3 days before delivery)
Server -> Server: Deadline Passed

Server -> System: Deadline Passed Error
System -> User: Display Error Message\n("Changes can only be made\n3 days before delivery")

@enduml
